Package: isnanReprex
Type: Package
Title: Minimal Reprex for TMB ISNAN Macro Bug with GCC C++17
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sam", "Johnson",
    email = "sdnjohnson@landmarkfisheries.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Demonstrates that the bare isnan() call inside TMB's
    ISNAN macro in tiny_ad/bessel/bessel.hpp fails under GCC with
    C++17 because isnan is not in the global namespace.  This
    package includes TMB.hpp and calls besselK() to trigger the
    macro expansion.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports: TMB, RcppEigen, Rcpp
LinkingTo: TMB, RcppEigen, Rcpp
